Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.GUI.controllers

Class PreviousGameController

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.GUI.controllers.FXMLController
it.polimi.ingsw.client.GUI.controllers.PreviousGameController
public class PreviousGameController extends FXMLController
PreviousGameController display a dialog scene that notifies the user that he was participating in a game before the server stopped. The user is asked to make a choice: resume the game or delete it.
